---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Financial & Decision Systems - intelio">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal mb-4 sm:mb-6">Financial & Decision Systems</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400">Real-time visibility into money, margins, and trade-offs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What Breaks (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What Breaks</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">Most organizations:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Close books late</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Lack real-time visibility into profitability</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Can't see margin by project, client, or segment</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Make financial decisions reactively</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Finance becomes historical reporting instead of a control system.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What We Build (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What We Build</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">We build financial and decision systems that connect operations to money.</p>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">This includes:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Job and project costing</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Margin and profitability analysis</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Cash flow tracking</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Forecasting and scenario modeling</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Executive dashboards grounded in operational data</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: How It Works (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">How It Works</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">We integrate financial data directly with operational activity, so leadership sees not just outcomes—but drivers.</p>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">AI is used for forecasting, trend detection, and scenario modeling where appropriate.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: The Impact (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">The Impact</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Clear financial truth</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Better capital allocation</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Fewer surprises</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Confident decision-making</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-8 sm:mb-12">Ready to see the real numbers?</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-black text-white text-base sm:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors min-h-[56px]">
        Work with Intelio
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

